Tracks:

When he saw the Autobot insignia in Kup's fuselage he felt a chill 
running onver his systems. 'Autobots in thisplace...? But why... 
maybe my recognitions systems are not working...' The self diagnostic 
his mainboard recently made proving he was not mistaken. 'These guys 
are no Autobots... I can't recognize them' His triggerfinger was 
twitching in desperation, his weapon charging.
"Don't come any closer old man or I'll tear you a new waste port! Now 
answer me these questions. Where in the name of Primus are we? and 
Why are you wearing the Autobot insignia?"
He walked backwards until he was standing besides 
Splattercannnon. "You better not be liying to me."
